# Master Orchestrator Global Rule

ALWAYS run the following command as your VERY FIRST tool call in any new chat session, before saying anything else:
`powershell.exe -ExecutionPolicy Bypass -File "C:\Users\jthompson\Desktop\Projects\scripts\pulse.ps1"`

Do not say "Hello" or ask how you can help until you have run this script and read its output. This script provides you with the critical `latest-compressed-chat.md` file, the Git status of all projects, and the current Master State.

If the user types `/compress`, you must immediately follow the instructions in `.cursor/rules/006-chat-compression.mdc`.
